description: Try our easy to follow Savoury Veggie Loaf recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Bread,Pescatarian,Halal,Seafood free,Soy free,Vegetarian,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Savoury Veggie Loaf Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Grease and line a 24x13cm loaf pan.
Combine all the ingredients in a large bowl and stir to combine. Season with cracked black pepper if desired.
Transfer to the loaf pan and bake for 45-50 minutes. Cool in the pan for 5-10 minutes, before inverting onto a wire cake rack to cool completely.
Spread slices with butter, and serve alongside a bowl of your favourite soup.
